      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds good in theory but sounds a bit optimistic lol. my margins are already super thin and i can't just magically make more money to cover everyone's higher pay. won't that just force me to raise my prices or maybe even cut staff just to stay afloat? i feel like you're ignoring the actual struggle of running a shop here.",
